                    <span>This book makes the art of mingling simple & fun! It really breaks down mingling into simple, easy, & proven techniques. I highly recommend this book along with 2 others: Fate & Reil's How to Have Sex with Hot Girls (without even dating them!) & Louis & Copeland's How to Succeed with Women.</span>
                  
